XML::Filter::XInclude
=====================

XInclude implemented as a simple SAX filter.

Simple to use:

  my $parser = XML::SAX::ParserFactor->parser(
    Handler => XML::Filter::XInclude->new(
        Handler => XML::SAX::Writer->new
    )
  );
  $parser->parse_uri("foo.xml");

Installation is same as any perl module:

 $ perl Makefile.PL
 $ make
 $ make test
 $ su
 $ make install

